headline: Oneok Inc. (OKE) Q3 Earnings Surpass Estimates
summary: Oneok (OKE) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +2.05% and -14.08%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: ONEOK Announces Higher Third Quarter 2025 Earnings and Affirms 2025 Net Income and Adjusted EBITDA Guidance Ranges
